487
01:33:41.451 --> 01:33:42.411
<b>MIYABI</b>

488
01:34:21.866 --> 01:34:22.666
<b>CURRICULUM VITAE</b>

489
01:35:00.238 --> 01:35:01.197
Miyabi?

490
